-Uncle. Uncle.
-Yes?

182
00:12:43,779 --> 00:12:45,576
This is the girl.

183
00:12:46,081 --> 00:12:47,878
l hope you know what you are doing.

184
00:12:48,684 --> 00:12:50,413
Waiter, have you a table for two?

185
00:12:50,586 --> 00:12:52,747
Sorry, no formal dress allowed.

186
